Z
h(n+N)=h(n)
n
m \in Z
\sum_{n=m}^{m+N-1} h(n) =\sum_{n=0}^{N-1} h(n)
N
m \in \{0 \dots, N-1\}
m \in \mathbb{Z}
m = kN + r
k \in \mathbb{Z}
r \in \{0, \dots, N-1\}
\sum_{n=0}^{N-1} h(n)
\sum_{n=m}^{m+N-1} h(n) = \sum_{n=m}^{N-1} h(n) + \sum_{n=0}^{m-1} h(n + N) = \sum_{n=m}^{N-1} h(n) + \sum_{n=0}^{m-1} h(n) = \sum_{n=0}^{N-1} h(n)
\sum_{n=kN+r}^{k(N+1) + r -1} h(n) = \sum_{n=r}^{N+r-1} h(n+kN) = \sum_{n=r}^{N+r-1} h(n)
